<BRK/>
<NPR>These paragraphs should be coordinated with Sections <SRF>43 13 13.13</SRF> VAPOR PHASE 
ACTIVATED CARBON ADSORPTION UNITS and <SRF>43 11 00</SRF> FANS/BLOWERS/PUMPS; OFF-GAS.</NPR><BRK/>
<BRK/>
