the type of testing to be performed, the date and time of testing, and the names of the Contractor's 
representatives who will be present.  Submit a plan for Completion Testing not more than [14] [_____] 
calendar days after requested.  Allow a period of not less than [30] [_____] calendar days in the schedule 
for Government review.  Address testing requirements for determining if regulatory clean-up criteria 
have been met, and for determining if the SVE system can be permanently shut down in the plan.</LST><BRK/>
